# =============================================================================
# AUTODESK PLATFORM SERVICES CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Service Account Authentication (for most tools)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# These credentials are used for automated, long-running access to most ACC
# functionality including projects, files, issues, and diagnostics.
# Requires: Server-to-Server application type in APS
APS_CLIENT_ID=your_service_account_app_client_id
APS_CLIENT_SECRET=your_service_account_app_client_secret

# Service Account Details (created using create-service-account script)
APS_SA_ID=your_service_account_id
APS_SA_EMAIL=your_service_account_email
APS_SA_KEY_ID=your_service_account_key_id
APS_SA_PRIVATE_KEY=your_service_account_private_key

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OAuth Authentication (for forms and user-accountable operations)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# These credentials enable user-based authentication for operations that require
# individual accountability, such as forms access, safety inspections, etc.
# Requires: Web Application type in APS with callback URL configured
APS_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=your_oauth_app_client_id
APS_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=your_oauth_app_client_secret

# =============================================================================
# SETUP NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 1. You need TWO separate APS applications:
#    - One "Server-to-Server" app for service account authentication
#    - One "Web Application" app for OAuth authentication
#
# 2. The OAuth app must have this callback URL configured:
#    http://localhost:8765/oauth/callback
#
# 3. Invite your service account email to your ACC projects as a member
#
# 4. See README.md for detailed setup instructions